📊 Poverty Ranking Analysis in Central Java 2020
Project Description:
This project presents a poverty ranking analysis of regencies and cities in Central Java in 2020 using data from Statistics Indonesia (BPS).
The analysis was conducted to identify regions with the highest and lowest poverty rates and to understand the distribution of poverty levels across Central Java.
The results are presented through tables and charts to provide a clear overview of poverty conditions and regional disparities.

Project Objectives:
Analyze poverty levels in Central Java in 2020.
Compare poverty rates among regencies and cities.
Identify regions with the highest and lowest poverty levels.
Present findings through tables and visualizations.
Develop data analysis skills using Microsoft Excel.

